  <description type="morphology">Stems 3–5 dm.  Leaves widely spaced proximally, becoming clustered to whorled near inflorescence; blade 1–8 cm.  Inflorescences with inflated rachises (rays) and peduncle.  Flowers: calyx 3–10 mm, longer than corolla; corolla white, 3–6 mm.  Capsules 1.5–3 mm.  Seeds 0.4–0.6 mm.  2n = 22.</description>
